  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro Rally takes you on a journey through the dusty roads of the past, whether you're a seasoned racer or a newcomer eager to dive into this legendary world. Prepare for a ride full of speed and excitement, as you push your limits against iconic cars and tough competitors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/f0b475b48e9a991a1da59b8f48340e37.poster.avif?t=1767384662\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/f0b475b48e9a991a1da59b8f48340e37.webm?t=1767384662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/f0b475b48e9a991a1da59b8f48340e37.mp4?t=1767384662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the passion of rally with 18 legendary playable rally cars and 14 different maps! Each car will push you to the limits of speed and control, while each map offers unique challenges and strategic opportunities, making you strive for greatness at every turn. Get ready for a journey filled with speed and adrenaline!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/bacd78a93715890c4a9d898bbf9e06fd.poster.avif?t=1767384662\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/bacd78a93715890c4a9d898bbf9e06fd.webm?t=1767384662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/bacd78a93715890c4a9d898bbf9e06fd.mp4?t=1767384662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
